<br>
From Safehouse:<br>
'if you have down to mavien, you get to a t junciton, if you go left instead of right (just before the first high guardian of justice), all the mob's in there are on creatures faction.<br>
<br>
if you head towards the trials, and take a right instead of a left at the t junction, all the prisioners in that section are on the prisions of justice faction.'<br>
<br>
